OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FThe headteacher of a school in Kent
OL,8,Fhas told ITV Meridian that it is still
OL,9,Fowed tens of thousands of pounds in
OL,10,Fcompensation after South East Water
OL,11,F(SEW) supply outages which impacted
OL,12,Fthousands of customers.
OL,14,FThe Skinners' Kent Academy Principal
OL,15,FHannah Knowles said the school lost
OL,16,Faround #30,000 as a result of the
OL,17,Foutages. This amount rises to #35,000
OL,18,Fwhen combined with losses from a third
OL,19,Fparty catering company, which operates
OL,20,Fin the school
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
