OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FMs Knowles' school is among 16 in the
OL,8,Farea which have reached out to Kent
OL,9,FCounty Council to retrieve
OL,10,Fcompensation on their behalf from SEW,
OL,11,Fthe authority told ITV Meridian.
OL,13,FIn recent months, tens of thousands of
OL,14,Fhouseholds and business were left
OL,15,Fwithout water supply across Kent and
OL,16,FSussex due to repeated outages.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
