OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FTunbridge Wells suffered a sustained
OL,8,Foutage in November and December, with
OL,9,Faround 24,000 properties in and around
OL,10,Fthe Kent town left without drinkable
OL,11,Fwater for almost two weeks.
OL,13,FSEW said it is "deeply sorry" for the
OL,14,Fimpact caused by the outages on
OL,15,Fresidents and businesses, adding that
OL,16,Fschools will be eligible for a
OL,17,Fcompensation fund separate from
OL,18,Fexisting payments.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FMs Knowles, speaking to ITV Meridian,
OL,8,Fsaid that her school had incurred
OL,9,Flosses due to several reasons,
OL,10,Fincluding having to buy portable
OL,11,Ftoilets and being unable to rent out
OL,12,Fschool facilities.
OL,14,F"We had two periods of time where we
OL,15,Fhad to close, so we're talking in the
OL,16,Fregion of #30,000 worth of losses," Ms
OL,17,FKnowles said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,F"And that came across at catering
OL,8,Flosses, letting losses, the fact that
OL,9,Fwe had to go out and buy some
OL,10,Fportaloos, just in case it (supply
OL,11,Foutages) continued.
OL,13,F"And #30,000 is the equivalent
OL,14,Factually of one teacher's salary, so
OL,15,Fit's significant.
OL,17,F"And at the minute we're bearing the
OL,18,Fbrunt of that financial cost for
OL,19,Fsomething that is not our fault, and
OL,20,Ffundamentally it gets me so angry that
OL,21,Fwe find ourselves in this position."
OL,26,@rD@\pmsD@Hpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
