PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FSEW said that as schools fall under
OL,8,Fits non-household customer category,
OL,9,Fthey would have received Guaranteed
OL,10,FStandards Scheme (GSS) payments from
OL,11,Ftheir water retailer like other
OL,12,Fbusinesses.
OL,14,FGSS is compensation paid automatically
OL,15,For upon request by UK water companies
OL,16,Fto customers when they fail to meet
OL,17,Fminimum service standards.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FIt added that schools will be eligible
OL,8,Ffor a separate fund that is being
OL,9,Festablished, but did not provide a
OL,10,Ftimescale for when that will be
OL,11,Favailable.
OL,13,FSEW said the additional fund takes the
OL,14,F"total package of compensation to
OL,15,Fbusinesses up to #2.5 million".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
