PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FHowever, Tunbridge Wells MP Mike
OL,8,FMartin told ITV Meridian that analysis
OL,9,Fby his office had shown losses
OL,10,Fincurred by businesses in the
OL,11,FTunbridge Wells area alone are around
OL,12,F#18.6 million.
