PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FA SEW spokesperson said: "We are
OL,8,Fdeeply sorry for the impact the supply
OL,9,Finterruption has had on residents and
OL,10,Fbusinesses in Tunbridge Wells.
OL,12,F"We abide by our Guaranteed Standards
OL,13,Fof Service (GSS) and want to ensure
OL,14,Fthat every single customer and
OL,15,Fbusiness receives exactly what they
OL,16,Fare entitled to under the scheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,F"All customers will have received
OL,8,Fcompensation in line with our
OL,9,FGuaranteed Standards of Service (GSS),
OL,10,Fwhich is accessible to customers and
OL,11,Fbusinesses on our website.
OL,13,F"We know how difficult this outage was
OL,14,Ffor businesses. Compensation has been
OL,15,Fpaid to their water retailer and we
OL,16,Fasked retailers to credit business
OL,17,Faccounts immediately.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,F"It is the retailers' responsibility
OL,8,Fto credit this compensation. We would
OL,9,Furge any business who has not received
OL,10,Fit to contact their water retailer.
OL,12,F"On top of the GSS guided payments, we
OL,13,Fare establishing a separate fund for
OL,14,Fbusinesses that faced specific
OL,15,Ffinancial losses.
OL,17,F"This will be managed independently,
OL,18,Fand we will share details on how to
OL,19,Fapply shortly. This takes the total
OL,20,Fpackage of compensation to businesses
OL,21,Fup to #2.5 million.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775127603
OL,3,CHeadteacher says school owed #30k
OL,4,Ccompensation after South East Water
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,F"Once again we are very sorry to all
OL,8,Fcustomers and businesses for the
OL,9,Fdisruption this caused and are working
OL,10,Fat pace to complete our six-month
OL,11,FResilience Plan of engineering works
OL,12,Fand operational changes as outlined
OL,13,Fearlier this month."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
